10
00:04:46,150 --> 00:04:47,110
Bai Sanxing.

11
00:04:52,590 --> 00:04:53,430
Bai Sanxing.

12
00:05:14,420 --> 00:05:15,710
Adakah saya memberitahu anda untuk membunuhnya?

13
00:05:16,910 --> 00:05:17,910
Bai Sanxing bukan milik anda

14
00:05:17,910 --> 00:05:18,750
