21
00:05:52,230 --> 00:05:53,070
Selepas siasatan,

22
00:05:53,420 --> 00:05:54,670
bukti adalah muktamad.

23
00:05:56,150 --> 00:05:57,710
Ketua pelakunya, Yan Zhang,

24
00:05:58,420 --> 00:06:00,380
