28
00:06:07,620 --> 00:06:08,940
dan memburu rakan sejenayah Yan.

29
00:06:09,300 --> 00:06:11,500
Padamkan boneka yang tinggal

30
00:06:11,500 --> 00:06:12,500
secepat mungkin.

31
00:06:13,180 --> 00:06:15,150
Mana-mana roh yang menimbulkan masalah

32
00:06:15,820 --> 00:06:17,260
juga mesti dihukum oleh undang-undang.

33
00:06:19,180 --> 00:06:20,940
Ya, Yang Mulia.

34
00:06:22,180 --> 00:06:23,020
Yang Mulia,

35
00:06:23,150 --> 00:06:24,790
bagaimana anda akan berurusan dengan Bai Sanxing?

36
00:06:25,260 --> 00:06:26,420
Dia menelan begitu ramai saudara

37
00:06:26,570 --> 00:06:27,420
